longBusinessSummary: Oi Wah Pawnshop Credit Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of secured financing services in Hong Kong. It offers pawn, mortgage loans, and money lending services, as well as consulting services. The company was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Oi Wah Pawnshop Credit Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Kwan Lik Holding Limited.
